<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="mental-adj">mental <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'mentl/    美 /'mentl/  </p>
<p>[只用于名词前]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>思想上的；精神的；脑力的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>mental labour
脑力劳动</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It's important to maintain good <strong>mental health</strong>.
保持心理健康很重要。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>mentally /'mentəli/ adv   </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Mentally, I began making a list of things I had to do.
我开始在脑子里盘算我该做哪些事情。</p></div></div>